      "span_text": "The differences between [CITATION_1] and our paper are as follows: 1) We present a black-box attack, in which the adversary doesn't need prior knowledge about the malware classifier, which makes our attack more feasible. 2) We don't modify existing API calls, because while such an attack is relevant for reviews -it might damage a malware functionality which we wish to avoid."
